  "title": "Savory Middle Eastern Fennel Sausage Stir-fry",
  "description": "A savory and tender brunch-mood dish featuring vegetarian-friendly Italian fennel sausages, with a touch of Middle Eastern flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern, Italian",
